Interface Summary

Class Summary
ProximityEntry Object representing a proximate device

The SDK will pass an ProximityEntry object in events when a proximate device has a change in status.
ProximityManager This class implements a wrapper to M87 Proximity SDK for apps.
ProximityManager.Event Defines codes and status for unsolicited events from MWC.
ProximityManager.Status Defines status codes for various actions requested by the application.
